<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>

<head>

<title>For Ayu ❤️</title>

<style>

body{

 margin:0;

 font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;

 background:#111;

 color:white;

 text-align:center;

 overflow-x:hidden;

}

.container{

 padding:40px 20px;

}

button{

 background:#ff4d88;

 border:none;

 color:white;

 padding:15px 30px;

 border-radius:30px;

 font-size:18px;

 cursor:pointer;

}

.hidden{

 display:none;

}

h1{

 font-size:38px;

}

.card{

 background:#222;

 padding:20px;

 border-radius:20px;

 margin:25px auto;

 max-width:500px;

}

img{

 width:90%;

 border-radius:20px;

 margin:15px;

}

.heart{

 position:fixed;

 animation:fall 5s linear infinite;

}

@keyframes fall{

 from{top:-20px;}

 to{top:100vh;}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Hey Ayu 👀❤️</h1>

<p>

I made something small for you...

</p>

<button onclick="openLove()">

Open it 💌

</button>

<div id="love" class="hidden">

<div class="card">

<h2>

My favorite person ❤️

</h2>

<p>

From random moments, silly laughs,

until becoming husband & wife...

</p>

<p>

27 June became my favorite date.

</p>

</div>

<img src="foto1.jpg">

<img src="foto2.jpg">

<div class="card">

<h2>

A little reminder 🤍

</h2>

<p>

Thank you for staying with me.

<br><br>

You are my home,

my partner in crime,

and the person I choose everyday.

</p>

<p>

(also... sorry ya harus tahan sama tingkah aku 🤣)

</p>

</div>

<img src="foto3.jpg">

<h2>

Forever us ❤️

</h2>

</div>

</div>

<script>

function openLove(){

document.getElementById("love")

.classList.remove("hidden");

for(let i=0;i<30;i++){

let h=document.createElement("div");

h.innerHTML="❤️";

h.className="heart";

h.style.left=Math.random()*100+"%";

h.style.animationDuration=

(3+Math.random()*5)+"s";

document.body.appendChild(h);

}

}

</script>

</body>

</html>